1. *Govori* se da će biti loša sezona. (It is said that it will be a bad season.)
2. Ona *govori* da će biti uspešna. (She speaks that she will be successful.)
3. Ja *govorim* da ona nije u pravu. (I am saying that she is not right.)
4. Oni su *govorili* da ćemo uspeti. (They were saying that we will succeed.)
5. Mi smo *govorili* da će biti teško. (We were saying that it will be hard.)
6. Oni su *govorili* o nama. (They were talking about us.)